          <h3>Image Quality</h3>
          <p>The jump to a 1-inch sensor is massive. Night footage that would be mush on a phone or GoPro looks clean
            and professional here. Skin tones are natural and pleasing straight out of camera.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card card-plain">
          <h3>Vertical Workflows</h3>
          <p>The rotating screen isn't just a gimmick. It physically rotates the UI and changes aspect ratio, making it
            the fastest way to switch between YouTube (16:9) and TikTok (9:16) shooting.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card card-plain">
          <h3>Sound</h3>
          <p>Pair it with the DJI Mic 2 (which connects wirelessly without a receiver!) and you have a pro-level
            interview setup that fits in a jacket pocket.</p>
        </article>
